name: Artgerm style Lora
description:
Update v2:
Updated my captions and lora training methods.

Use cg for a cleaner look or stylize for a more artsy feel, combining the two work great too.

Using realistic adds a lot of detail, but may warp (and sometimes fix) anatomy.

Use traditional media for a marker/drawing style.

Version 1:

Works best with the anything-v4.5 model

Weight around 0.6 works best for me, anything below 1 seems to work

was trained to work with clip skip 2, but works well with skip 1
